title: JCU Townsville
body:
Better get it started for JCU in Townsville to see if anyone on campus is interested in forming a team. 
Email andrew.ryan1@my.jcu.edu.au 
Please ensure that you are registered to the Townsville campus (internal would be preferred) and include your rank as well (in case more than 7 are interested) 
Check out the OUC rules booklet attached at the top of the main discussion board. 

Thanks
Andi
